aly in the imperial period (see LGPN 3A: 177).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":227,"html":228},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Ferrua 1989 119 no.455 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001995\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 185 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":230,"html":231},"handnote","\u003Cp>Irregular letters, A and Λ with serifs, A with slanting bar, lunate Ε, Υ like the Latin V, cursive Ω.\u003C/p> Lines 1-2  50-80  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  ",{"id":233,"html":234},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[236,238,241,242],{"html":237},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo, Alex Antoniou",{"id":239,"lang":122,"html":240},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐτραπελίων\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐτραπελίων\">Εὐτραπε-\u003Cbr id=\"al2-interpretive\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>λ̣ί̣ων\u003C/span>\u003C/span> ☧ \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>",{"html":237},{"id":243,"lang":122,"html":244},"edition-diplomatic","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐτραπελίων\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐτραπελίων\">ΕΥΤΡΑΠΕ\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"